Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) before working in this repo. Key points:

- This repo's path contains `&`, which breaks npm `.bin` shims and `npx` on
  Windows — invoke tools via `node node_modules/<pkg>/<bin>.js` or the npm
  scripts (which already do this).
- Agent skills live in `.claude/skills/` — they are plain markdown and are
  the source of truth for component and docs work (see the other rules in
  this folder for when each applies).
- `chart-tool-echarts/` is a separate Vite app (the data-viz tool deployed at
  cake.lenovo.com/dataviz) with its own docs, scripts, and tests.
